data.description: Enjoy the perfect blend of country & city life with this spectacular Bella Vista area home on a 1-acre lot. Immaculate & well-maintained, this home offers 4 bedrooms, 3 baths with 3281 sf of ample living space. The galley style kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, tile flooring & eating space. Other features include formal dining, 3 living areas perfect for entertaining, a dedicated cedar-lined room with a hot tub that's been recently serviced & an oversized 2-car garage with plenty of room for additional parking. Newer HVAC system with a transferrable 5-year warranty, freshly stained decking, low maintenance front landscaping with drip system for plants & trees. Fully fenced backyard offers territorial views, several fruit trees & additional 7' fenced area for horses, chickens, or??? No HOA's - possibilities are endless, schedule your private tour today!
